resources.string: Unduh dan instal fitur tambahan untuk Cover Tampilan LED. Anda dapat membuat ikon LED sendiri dan mengaturnya sebagai ikon notifikasi. Untuk mengunduhnya nanti, buka Pengaturan > Fitur lanjutan > Aksesori > Cover tampilan LED, lalu pilih Unduh fitur tambahan.

Download and install additional features for LED View Cover. You can create your own LED icons and set them as your notification icons. To download them later, go to Settings > Accessories > LED View Cover, then select Download additional features.
